OL,3,CWales' second home rules made us
OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,FA woman who was born and raised in
OL,8,FPembrokeshire says she's had to
OL,9,Fconsider selling a house that's been
OL,10,Fin her family for half a century to
OL,11,Fforeign investors because of the Welsh
OL,12,FGovernment's second home policy.
OL,14,FAnna Raymond and her two sisters are
OL,15,Fkeeping a family tradition by running
OL,16,Fthe Pantyderi Manor in Boncath as a
OL,17,Fself-catering holiday let, but Anna
OL,18,Ffears that the government's rules are
OL,19,Fthreatening the future of the much-
OL,20,Floved house she inherited from her
OL,21,Fgrandparents.
