OL,3,CWales' second home rules made us
OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,FFrom April 2023 holiday-let owners who
OL,8,Fwant to qualify for business rates
OL,9,Finstead of council tax must fill the
OL,10,Fproperty for 182-days. The threshold
OL,11,Fused to be 70.
OL,13,FIf Anna fails to reach the 182-day
OL,14,Fthreshold, she will fail to qualify
OL,15,Ffor business tax, and as Pantyderi is
OL,16,Fher second property, it, therefore,
OL,17,Fqualifies for the council tax premium.
