OL,3,CWales' second home rules made us
OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,FFrom 2023, Welsh councils have the
OL,8,Fpower to introduce a council tax
OL,9,Fpremium of up to 300% for second homes
OL,10,Fand empty homes. Pembrokeshire council
OL,11,Frecently voted to increase the premium
OL,12,Fto 200% from April. If Anna isn't able
OL,13,Fto fill Pantyderi for 182 days a year,
OL,14,Fshe could face a council tax bill of
OL,15,Faround #12,000.
OL,17,FSpeaking to S4C's current affairs
OL,18,Fprogramme Y Byd ar Bedwar Anna says
OL,19,Fthat the policy is "unfair".
