OL,3,CWales' second home rules made us
OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,F"The 182-day threshold is very high,
OL,8,Fit's a lot - I would like someone to
OL,9,Fbe here every day of the year. We work
OL,10,Fhard, but realistically, we are in the
OL,11,Fmiddle of the countryside, it would be
OL,12,Fharder for us to get the 182 days.
OL,14,F"I don't know where they get the
OL,15,Ffigure of 182 but it is much too high,
OL,16,Fso before it was 70, so they more than
OL,17,Fdoubled that figure and more... It is
OL,18,Fnot fair."
