OL,3,CWales' second home rules made us
OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,FPantyderi Manor has 10 rooms that
OL,8,Fsleeps 21 guests, and Anna's late
OL,9,Fgrandparents ran the Manor as a Bed
OL,10,Fand Breakfast.
OL,12,FAnna and her family have no plans to
OL,13,Fsell Pantyderi Manor, but a recent
OL,14,Foffer from an Iranian investor who
OL,15,Foffered millions for the house made
OL,16,Fher think twice about the future.
OL,18,F"They wouldn't care how many nights
OL,19,Fthey were here," said Anna.
