OL,7,FAnna is determined to keep Pantyderi
OL,8,Fin the family but fears that other
OL,9,Fowners of historical Welsh homes may
OL,10,Fhave to take offers from buyers
OL,11,Foutside Wales.
OL,13,FAlthough the policy is intended to
OL,14,Fcreate a fair housing market, Anna
OL,15,Fsays that many of the second homes
OL,16,Fthat are run as self-catering
OL,17,Faccommodation are too expensive for
OL,18,Flocal people.
