OL,7,FTackling second homes was one of the
OL,8,Fmain issues of the Collaboration Plan
OL,9,Fbetween the Welsh Government and Plaid
OL,10,FCymru in 2021. However, speaking on Y
OL,11,FByd ar Bedwar, Plaid Cymru MP, Ben
OL,12,FLake criticised the 182-day rule.
OL,14,F'Evidence and real experience'
OL,16,F"I want to see the Government look at
OL,17,Fthe evidence and real experience."
