OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,FMr Lake, who has represented Plaid
OL,8,FCymru in Westminster since 2017, said
OL,9,Fhe was not against setting a
OL,10,Fthreshold, but that it must be one
OL,11,Fthat is fair to businesses.
OL,13,FHe said that we must "ensure that we
OL,14,Fdon't see real businesses having to
OL,15,Fclose and very often, family
OL,16,Fbusinesses that have been running for
OL,17,Fdecades, have to give up because they
OL,18,Fcan't reach that threshold. "
