OL,3,CWales' second home rules made us
OL,4,Cconsider selling home to Middle East
OL,5,Cinvestors
OL,7,FMr Lake said that the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment's intention is a valid one
OL,9,Fbut that more flexibility needs to be
OL,10,Fintroduced which differentiates
OL,11,Fbetween people who "take advantage of
OL,12,Fthe system, and real businesses.
OL,14,F"It is only right that those who use
OL,15,Fthem as a second home pay the tax. I
OL,16,Fbelieve there is an important
OL,17,Fdifference between the businesses that
OL,18,Fhave diversified and those who have
OL,19,Fthen bought residential houses in
OL,20,Ftowns and villages for the sole reason
OL,21,Fof making quick money."
