OL,7,FIn a consultation in 2021, the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment asked the public what the
OL,9,Fnew threshold should be. Of the 900
OL,10,Frespondents, 9 had suggested 182 days
OL,11,For six months of the year.
OL,13,FAccording to the Welsh Government, the
OL,14,Fthreshold reflects their policy that
OL,15,Fself-catering accommodation should be
OL,16,Foperating as businesses for at least
OL,17,Fhalf the year to qualify for business
OL,18,Ftaxes.
OL,20,F'Fair housing market'
