OL,7,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"The changes to the local tax rules
OL,9,Ffor self-catering accommodation and
OL,10,Fsecond homes are designed to help
OL,11,Fdevelop a fairer housing market and
OL,12,Fensure property owners make a fair
OL,13,Fcontribution to the communities where
OL,14,Fthey own homes or run businesses.
OL,16,F"We believe that everybody has a right
OL,17,Fto a decent, affordable home to buy or
OL,18,Fto rent in their own communities so
OL,19,Fthey can live and work locally.
